3. Mapbuzz Gold Subscription
Gold subscription gives users a Gold account which unlocks premium features.
You can cancel your Gold memberships at any time by going to your profile page > settings icon on the top > settings link at the bottom > you will find the cancel button here. 
        When you cancel your subscription it will end instantly. If you want to cancel your monthly subscription make sure you do it 24 hours prior to your billing date.
Android users can also cancel their subscription directly on the
Google Play's Subscription Center
